query:
SELECT v.id, v.formandoId, v.valorTotal / 100 as valor, v.excluido,
       DATE_FORMAT(v.dataVenda, '%d/%m/%Y') as data_venda
FROM vendas v 
WHERE DATE(v.dataVenda) = '2026-06-15'
  AND v.valorTotal = 50000
  AND v.valorLiquido = 50000
  AND v.excluido = 0
ORDER BY v.id
LIMIT 2
